439
00:46:47.513 --> 00:46:49.598
I let you live.

440
00:46:52.100 --> 00:46:53.769
- And you wasted it.
- No. no. no!

441
00:47:09.618 --> 00:47:11.078
Hey.

442
00:47:11.119 --> 00:47:13.079
- Shit.
